<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ shēng zhǎng zài nà biān, wǒ shēng zhǎng zài zhè biān,
 nǐ wǒ wèi xún qiú zhēn lǐ tà shàng yī tiáo de píng xiàn.
 nǐ bù céng rèn shì wǒ, wǒ yě méi yǒu hé nǐ jiàn guò miàn,
 nǐ wǒ què bèi shén zhào, xiāng rèn zài jīn tiān.
 nǐ wǒ cóng jīn bù zài mò shēng, shén yǐ jīng zài nǐ wǒ zhōng jiān,
 nǐ wǒ yào cháng cháng xǐ lè, hù xiāng quàn miǎn.
 zhǔ yǐ jīng jìn le, nǐ wǒ bù yào zài xián zhàn,
 yīng dāng yī wú guà lǜ, wèi zhǔ fèng xiàn,
 ràng nǐ wǒ yī qǐ zhàn lì qǐ lái, xié shǒu xiàng qián dēng pān.
 shān zài gāo dǎng bù zhù nǐ wǒ qián jìn de shuāng yǎn,
 hǎi làng zài xiōng yǒng dǎng bù zhù nǐ wǒ qián jìn de fēng fān.
 ràng nǐ wǒ bǐ cǐ xiāng ài yǔ shén miàn duì miàn.</lyrics>
<title>nǐ wǒ tóng xíng 迦南21</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>21</hymn_number>
</song>